Flight time from New York to Nicosia (CYPRUS) - Flight duration 11H25

As an indication, departures from New York to Nicosia are mainly at the two airports of New York. Flights from major cities in the USA are often possible. In all the best cases, the minimum flight time is 11H25 to cover a distance of 5.452 miles.
